title: The Prisoner [Special Edition] - EXTRAS - Village Map & Postcard
description:
The Prisoner [Special Edition] - EXTRAS - Village Map & Postcards

Hi-Res Map of The Village - sourced from a replica of the one used in the series that came with a Prisoner DVD magazine series several year ago. The map is almost 100cm x 50cm, scanned at 300 dpi - 11772 x 5252 pixels! Has to be the most difficult scanning/image compilation I have done to date!)

Postcards from The Village - sourced from the 35th (not 40th) Anniversary DVD boxed set, 5 &#039;Prisoner&#039; postcards - back and front.
